  "data": {
    "description": "<p>This skill targets the next scene. Make your [Athletics Check] once. Compare the result to every enemy appearing in the next scene's [Identification Difficulty]. For each success, you learn that enemy's name, appearance, rank, and tags. You take [Fatigue: (Base STR)].</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>(Fumble): The enemy notices your scouting.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A special skill that conducts preliminary reconnaissance before entering battle and conveys information about the enemy you encounter to your allies.</p>",
